<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$too-young" href="/people/too-young">涂样</a>，<strong title="我不是新闻工作者。" class="zu-question-my-bio">我不是新闻工作者。</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="21">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$tsugu-kiri" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/tsugu-kiri" class="zg-link" title="tsugu Kiri">tsugu Kiri</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$men-tu-qing-teng" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/men-tu-qing-teng" class="zg-link" title="姜树">姜树</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户</span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


